highlights.text: “愛人錯過” by 告五人 has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 173 days straight.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “Golden” is the highest at #5.
“有一种遗憾叫我们” by 田园 is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #87.
“no signal - super slowed” by juggsi and kyra is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 25 spots at #58.
